race.comment: SUNNY STRIDE (1) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. MAGIC LOKI (4) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (25.63) there the start prior. Can figure in the finish. MONTANA ICON (5) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (25.49) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Can measure up. HECTOR DARCY (8) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.
